Package: polygrams
Type: Package
Title: Density Estimation with Mixtures of Disjoint Bernstein Polynomials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jonas Moss
Maintainer: Jonas Moss <jonas.gjertsen@gmail.com>
Description: Density estimation with discrete mixtures of Bernstein 
    polynomials. Supports several shape constraints, and contains 
    routines for computing distribution functions, quantiles, and
    random number generation.
License: GPL-3
